<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <!--inline[../../../common/page/head.ejs]-->
    <title>第四天
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../static/genisis/days.css?_inline">
</head>
<body style="overflow:hidden" scroll="no" class="day4 blackFont">
    <img src="../../static/genisis/image/day4.jpg?__inline" alt="" class="bgimg day4-day">
    <div class="over">
        <div class="cloud cloud1"></div>
        <div class="cloud cloud2"></div>
        <div class="tree tree2"></div>
        <div class="star star1"></div>
        <div class="star star2"></div>
    </div>
    <img src="../../static/genisis/image/day4-night.jpg?__inline" alt="" class="bgimg day4-night">
    <div class="aside">
        <p>在你到达前的一个纪元，</p>
        <p>椰子大陆一片空虚与混沌···</p>
        <p>没有光明，没有生命，也没有苍穹··</p>
        <p>直到2016年伊始，造物主你的降临···</p>
    </div>
    <div class="take not">
     <div class="taskConent">
            <h4>降临大陆任务</h4>
            <span class="redfont">任务要求</span>
            <p>根据系统提示，完成绑定银行卡操作。</p>
            <span class="redfont">任务奖励</span>
            <p><img src="../../static/genisis/image/closeBox.png" alt="" class="taskBox">成为椰子大陆的造物主 体验金1000元。</p>
        </div> 
        <a href="#" class="btn">去完成任务</a>
    </div>
    <div class="take yes takeBg">
        <h4>降临大陆任务</h4>
        <p>绑定银行卡任务您已完成本任务</p>
        <p>完成获得奖励：成为椰子大陆的造物主体验金1000元</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn">继续前行</a>
    </div>
    <div class="take aleady takeBg">
        <p>绑定银行卡任务您已完成本任务</p>
        <p>完成获得奖励：成为椰子大陆的造物主体验金1000元</p>
    </div>
    <footer>
        <a class="home"></a>
        <a class="yesterday"></a>
        <span>第四天</span>
        <a class="tasklist"></a>
        <a class="tomorrow"></a>
    </footer>
    <!--inline[../../../common/page/foot.ejs]-->
    <script>
    $(function(){
        var state = 1;
        if(state == 0){
            $('.aside > p').animate({width: '100%'}, 3000);
            $('.not').show(1000);
            $('.taskConent').hide();
        }
        else if(state == 1){
            $('.yes').show(1000);
            showup();
        }
        else {
            $('.aleady').show(1000);
            showup();
        }
        $('.btn').click(function(){
            $('.not').addClass('takeBg');
            $('.taskConent').show(1000);
        });
        function showup(){
            $('.day4-day').animate({opacity: '1'}, 3000);
            $('.tree').addClass('tree3');
            $('.day4-night').addClass('day-night');
            $('.star1').addClass('starsprink');
            $('.star2').addClass('star2sprink')
        }
    });
    </script>
</body>
</html>